{"tid":1907564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙漠蝗蟲若氣候條件合適隨時殺入西藏雲南 林業及草原局急要求密切監測","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:51:42.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"321330b6822f7d51b6929ccb46354de8ff680ac3","tid":1907564,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>新冠肺炎疫情未結束，另一場天災又至，國家林業及草原局發出通知，指聯合國糧食及農業組織(FAO)專家認為，若氣候條件合適，始於非洲並已蔓延至印度和巴基斯坦的沙漠蝗蟲，可能會從印巴入侵西藏，或者經緬甸入侵雲南，又或者經哈薩克入侵新疆，雲南、西藏、新疆特別要高度關注、密切監測沙漠蝗蟲情況，做好邊境監控工作，及時上報沙漠蝗蟲任何重要變化、動態。<br />\n<br />\n通知又要求各省區市林業部門決不能有任何思想麻痹，掉以輕心，而針對今年國內外蝗情的複雜形勢，林業及草原局擬於本月召開「全國草原蝗災趨勢會商會」，分析發生草原蝗災的風險，及時部署做好草原蝗災防控工作。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%9D%97%E8%9F%B2%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A5%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E9%9B%B2%E5%8D%97-%E6%9E%97%E8%8D%89%E5%B1%80%E6%80%A5%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%AC-209590?fbclid=IwAR0ciVC5YISL-DD5B8naUd36OPhRqn6jX5YooAWtGmOLhQa7-DIDOLM8c_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E6%25BC%25A0%25E8%259D%2597%25E8%259F%25B2%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%259B%25B2%25E5%258D%2597-%25E6%259E%2597%25E8%258D%2589%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%2588%2587%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%25B8%25AC-209590%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ciVC5YISL-DD5B8naUd36OPhRqn6jX5YooAWtGmOLhQa7-DIDOLM8c_Q&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=0e2449c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E8%9D%97%E8%9F%B2%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A5%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E9%9B%B2%E5%8D%97-%E6%9E%97%E8%8D%89%E5%B1%80%E6%80%A5%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%9B%A3%E6%B8%AC-209590?fbclid=IwAR0ciVC5YISL-DD5B8naUd36OPhRqn6jX5YooAWtGmOLhQa7-DIDOLM8c_Q</a>"},